TDD exercise complete. All 11 tests pass:
- Empty grid handling
- Rule 1 (Underpopulation): single cell + two adjacent cells die
- Rule 2 (Survival): cells with 2 or 3 neighbors survive
- Rule 3 (Overpopulation): center of full 3x3 dies
- Rule 4 (Reproduction): dead cell with 3 neighbors becomes alive
- Patterns: blinker oscillates, block stable, negative coordinates, single cell

